column5: NVTA You need to know if you have the brca gene for PANCREATIC cancer not just breat cancer How do find it INVITAE Lynparza significantly delayed disease progression as 1stline maintenance treatment in germline BRCAmutated metastatic pancreatic cancer

NVTA there are certain times you can look around the corner and see the future In very few of these cases can you profit from it This is one of those cases The case for DTC genomic testing for all people is evident 16 of us have ACTIONABLE diseases that we dont know about Invitae is boldly taking us to the inevitable future IBB ILMN
